<title>USA: One Price Clothing's Jacobs resigns as CEO.</title>
<headline>One Price Clothing's Jacobs resigns as CEO.</headline>
<dateline>DUNCAN, S.C. 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>One Price Clothing Stores Inc Chairman, President and Chief Executive Henry Jacobs said Tuesday he is resigning as president and chief executive but will continue as chairman of the board.</p>
<p>The company said Larry Kelley has accepted the positions of president and chief executive.  Kelley will also serve as a member of the board, the company said.</p>
<p>Prior to joining the company, Kelley was the president and chief executive of Casual Male Big and Tall, a division of J. Baker Inc.</p>
